{"tid":1899050,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【南韓疫情】南韓政府：可重覆使用低污染口罩","createTime":"2020-02-26T11:02:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-26T11:17:42.000Z","uid":161430,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7be6e9f7ca815f5be516edbbd826a778ff3efc13","tid":1899050,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T11:02:39.000Z","msg":"南韓新型冠狀病毒肺炎（武漢肺炎）疫情惡化，南韓民眾紛紛四出買口罩抗疫。在口罩短缺的情況下，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>南韓政府竟然建議民眾可重用部份自用口罩，籲民眾可自行判斷那些口罩的污染程度較低，以重覆使用口罩。</strong></span>不過，香港醫生強調外科手術口罩不宜用重，大家切勿亂試。<br />\n<br />\n大邱大批民眾周一到當地連鎖超市E-mart搶購口罩，人龍可謂一望無際。南韓衛生部門據報與E-mart合作穩住口罩供應，以半價賣口罩。每人購買口罩的數量受限，故不少南韓人全家總動員齊齊排隊買口罩。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.fmkorea.com/files/attach/new/20161009/2895716/272648202/480815111/67ed5bcbacebf35c5618c6820bb1f6a4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.fmkorea.com%2Ffiles%2Fattach%2Fnew%2F20161009%2F2895716%2F272648202%2F480815111%2F67ed5bcbacebf35c5618c6820bb1f6a4.jpg&h=19a07f94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n南韓食品醫藥品安全處處長李儀卿周二指，南韓現時每日生產達1,100萬個口罩，較前兩周多一倍，但仍出現供應短缺。"},{"pid":"b0bd5b2eac9a8830172ed7a75ac1f409493f425d","tid":1899050,"uid":37596,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T11:04:37.000Z","msg":"泡菜叫人洗手好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7426f98a7ddb32053bae6b1304f854361412cf18","tid":1899050,"uid":161430,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"b0bd5b2eac9a8830172ed7a75ac1f409493f425d","tid":1899050,"uid":37596,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T11:04:37.000Z","msg":"泡菜叫人洗手好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T11:07:11.000Z","msg":"叫人唔好再周街吐痰好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83d0e1ba664f2a56e499129d3f9c4342ffc53391","tid":1899050,"uid":77092,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T11:07:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid"